OL,4,CWomen's state pension: Compensation
OL,5,Ccloser for Waspi campaigners
OL,6, Government officials were too slow to
OL,7, tell many women they would be affected
OL,8, by the rising state pension age, the
OL,9, Parliamentary Ombudsman has ruled.
OL,11,FThe finding brings the prospect of
OL,12,Fcompensation closer for thousands of
OL,13,Fwomen born in the 1950s who have long
OL,14,Fbeen furious about the issue.
OL,16,FIt marks a significant victory for the
OL,17,FWaspi (Women Against State Pension
OL,18,FInequality) campaign.
OL,20,FHowever, the ombudsman has no power to
OL,21,Frefund "lost" pensions.
